colibri-mt
------------------------------------------
Machine Translation framework that wraps around the Moses Decoder and enables
k-NN classifier techniques to be used for modelling source-side-context

Runtime requirements:
  cygwin-3.3.5-1
  libcolibricore0-2.5.5-1bl1
  libcolibrimt-devel-0.2-1bl2
  libcolibrimt0-0.2-1bl2
  libgcc1-11.3.0-1
  libstdc++6-11.3.0-1
  pkg-config-1.8.0-1
  zlib0-1.2.12-1

Build requirements:
(besides corresponding -devel packages)
  autoconf-15-1
  automake-11-1
  binutils-2.38-1
  cygport-0.35.1-1
  gcc-core-11.3.0-1
  gcc-g++-11.3.0-1
  libcolibricore-devel-2.5.5-1bl1
  libtool-2.4.7-1
  make-4.3-1
  zlib-devel-1.2.12-1

Canonical website:
  https://github.com/proycon/colibri-mt

Canonical download:
  https://github.com/proycon/colibri-mt/archive/refs/tags/v0.2.tar.gz

-------------------------------------------

Build instructions:
  1. unpack colibri-mt-0.2-X-src.tar.xz
  2. if you use setup to install this src package,
     it will be unpacked under /usr/src automatically
        % cd /usr/src
        % cygport ./colibri-mt-0.2-X.cygport all

This will create:
  /usr/src/colibri-mt-0.2-X-src.tar.xz
  /usr/src/colibri-mt-0.2-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libcolibrimt0-0.2-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libcolibrimt-devel-0.2-X.tar.xz

-------------------------------------------

Files included in the binary package:

(colibri-mt)
  /usr/bin/colibri-mosesphrasetable2alignmodel.exe
  /usr/share/doc/Cygwin/colibri-mt.README
  /usr/share/doc/colibri-mt/AUTHORS
  /usr/share/doc/colibri-mt/COPYING

(libcolibrimt0)
  /usr/bin/cygcolibrimt-0.dll

(libcolibrimt-devel)
  /usr/include/colibri-mt/gzstream.h
  /usr/include/colibri-mt/lm.h
  /usr/lib/libcolibrimt.dll.a
  /usr/lib/pkgconfig/colibri-mt.pc

